title: AFC South Breakdown + Hidden Values, Jackhammer! - Fantasy Football Podcast for 7/19
description:
On today’s fantasy football podcast, a 2022 preview for the AFC South division! Is Derrick Henry a high-risk draft pick? What impact will Matt Ryan have on the Colts? Plus, find out which players on the Texans and Jaguars could be hidden values in fantasy football drafts! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for July 19th, 2022
